      "content": "thanks. i tried drinking some water but it's hard to focus. i feel like my arm is a bit heavy too, but i've probably just been swimming too much. should i just take some ibuprofen and nap it off? i really don't want to go to a hospital if i can avoid it, it seems like i just need to cool down.",
